item.title: CVE-2023-44219|2023-10-27T07:22:35.702Z -- sonicwall -- directory%20services%20connector
item.description: A local privilege escalation vulnerability in SonicWall Directory Services Connector Windows MSI client 4.1.21 and earlier versions allows a local low-privileged user to gain system privileges through running the recovery feature.
